{{Quote|Nitwit! These are not the bones of sea serpents! These are the bones of all my ruined hopes, strewn about this barren rock! I name this island 'Binks's Woe!'|[[George R. Binks]]|<ref name="George R. Binks (comic)">{{Tales|20|George R. Binks}}</ref>}}
'''Binks's Woe''' was an island in the southernmost seas of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. [[Jar Jar Binks's father|George R. Binks]], his [[Jar Jar Binks's mother|wife]] and their son [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar]] spent at least a month shipwrecked there.<ref name="GRB" />

